ILI TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in May rose 38.45% to NT$815,649,000 from NT$589,128,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            815,649          589,128    
YOY%              38.45%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           3,670,663        3,113,530   
YOY%              17.89% 
=================================================================
 